                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/3653" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0316</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9129 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">路漫漫其修远兮—中恒集团“稳中求变”进行人资升级</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Still a Long Way Ahead: The Upgrading of Human Resource in Zhongheng Group</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">覃大嘉，呼玲妍，崔鼎昌，刘人怀</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杭州电子科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广西梧州中恒集团股份有限公司 </td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源；招聘；培训；企业大学；文化</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> Human Resource; Recruitment; Training; Enterprise University; Culture</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2016年1月底，处于困境中的中恒集团被广投集团收购，并组建了新领导班子，确立了新战略目标：“致力于制药与健康领域的传承与创新，提升人类生命质量体验，将中恒集团打造成为医药健康产业综合集团”，并将“人力资源优化与升级”定调为最紧迫的基础工作。这是因为，当时的人资管理系统较为混乱，员工士气低落且离职率高，更缺少高素质人才储备。本案例详述了崔副总裁如何带领人资团队挑战这个艰巨的战略任务，如何运用稳中求变的方式来进行人资变革，如何从最根本的招聘与培训入手，逐步推进人资优化与升级，协助公司建立优秀、稳定的人才队伍。本案例主要聚焦于探讨人力资源管理有关招聘、培训和企业文化模块的优化与升级实践，突显出战略人力资源管理对组织变革的重要性，也为其他进行变革的企业提供借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In the end of January 2016, GuangTou Group acquired control of Zhongheng that was in deep trouble and built a new top management team, who then proposed their strategic goal: &quot;Focusing on the inheritance and innovation in the fields of pharmacy and health sciences, improving the quality of human life, and making Zhongheng a competitive and comprehensive business group in this line &quot;.  The upgrading and optimizing of human resource (HR) has been viewed as the most urgent mission for organizational change since then, considering the mess regarding the chaotic HR management system, low employee morale, high turnover rate and shortage of high-quality talents at that time.  This case elaborates on how the Vice President Dr. Tsuei has led the HR team to cope with this arduous challenge and to manage HR changes with a priority of stability; they started from the reform of the basic HR functions, namely the personnel recruitment and training, and then gradually propelled and deepened the HR reform to help the company develop a stable, high-quality workforce.  This case that draws our attention to the upgrading and optimizing of several HR modules (i.e., recruitment, training and the building of organizational culture) highlights the importance of strategic HR management for organizational change in practice; it also provides significant implications for other enterprises in China.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》、《组织行为学》、《管理学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略人力资源管理、人事规划与招募、员工培训与开发、劳动力多元化、员工激励、组织文化</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018-12</td>
                            </tr>
